---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/1003569689254137856
  Locus:
    Date: 4 Jun 2018
---
Some people consider the practice of love and compassion is only related
to religious practice and if they are not interested in religion they
neglect these inner values. But love and compassion are qualities that
human beings require just to live together.
